    to an existing test-file that illustrates the bug or desired feature.

SEE ALSO
    Other "End::Eval::*" (like End::Eval::FirstArg and End::Eval::Env) and
    "End::*" modules.

    Other "Devel::End::*" modules (but this namespace is deprecated in favor
    of "End").

